        <!-- 2. Description of Service -->
        <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>
          Evaluetor is an AI-powered contract intelligence platform that enables organizations to upload, analyze, and manage contracts throughout their lifecycle. The Service includes, but is not limited to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>AI-powered extraction of metadata, clauses, obligations, risks, and renewal terms from contracts</li>
          <li>Obligation tracking with deadline monitoring and compliance status</li>
          <li>SLA performance monitoring with breach detection and service credit calculation</li>
          <li>Renewal management with automated deadline alerts</li>
          <li>Relationship governance with KPI tracking and perception scoring</li>
          <li>Semantic search and AI-powered question answering over your contract corpus</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- 3. Account Registration -->
