        <p>You agree to use the Service only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You may:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Upload and analyze contracts for which you have the legal right to access and process</li>
          <li>Use extracted intelligence and analytics for your internal business purposes</li>
          <li>Share access with authorized members of your organization through the platform's access controls</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You may not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Upload documents containing illegal content or content that violates third-party rights</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or otherwise extract the source code of the platform or its AI models</li>
