        </p>
        <p>
          The AI-generated analysis and intelligence provided by the Service is for informational purposes and does not constitute legal advice. You are responsible for independently verifying any AI-extracted information before making business or legal decisions based on it.
        </p>

        <!-- 9. Termination -->
        <h2>9. Termination</h2>
        <p>
          Either party may terminate these Terms at any time by providing written notice. Upon termination, your right to access the Service will cease. You may export your Customer Data at any time during the active subscription period and for 30 days following termination.
        </p>
        <p>
          After the 30-day post-termination period, we will delete your Customer Data and all extracted intelligence from our systems, unless retention is required by applicable law. We will provide you with a data export in a standard, machine-readable format upon request.
        </p>
        <p>
          We may suspend or terminate your access immediately if you materially breach these Terms, including but not limited to violations of the Acceptable Use policy.
        </p>

